24805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsharer.php%3Fu%3Dhttp%253a%252f%252fwww.voachinese.com%252fcontent%252fun-china-tibet-20121102%252f1537983.html\">Facebook</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fsharing_help.html\">关于共享</a></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p><img class=\"photo\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://gdb.voanews.eu/5E03A15E-7B90-4834-8FEF-82DFA3B62B46_w268_r1_cx0_cy7_cw0.jpg\" /><span>联合国高级专员皮莱</span></p>\n<div>\n<p><span>x</span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.eu%2F5E03A15E-7B90-4834-8FEF-82DFA3B62B46_mw800_s.jpg\" title=\"联合国高级专员皮莱\"><img class=\"photo\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://gdb.voanews.eu/5E03A15E-7B90-4834-8FEF-82DFA3B62B46_w640_r1_s_cx0_cy7_cw0.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p><span>联合国高级专员皮莱</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p>联合国人权事务高级专员纳维皮莱敦促中国解决西藏地区普遍存在的不满情绪。民众的怨愤引发越来越多的流血抗议。<br /> <br />纳维皮莱星期五在一份声明中说，绝不可能通过高压的安全手段和压制人权的做法达到西藏社会稳定的目的。<br /> <br />纳维皮莱说，不断有人指控说，藏人因行使基本人权而遭到暴力镇压，她对此感到不安。<br /> <br />她同时呼吁藏人要自我克制，不要采取自焚等极端抗议行为。她还敦促宗教领袖利用自己的影响力帮助制止更多的人死于自焚。<br /> <br />自2009年2月以来，已发生至少62起藏人抗议中国西藏政策的自焚事件，至少有50名抗议者在自焚中丧生。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/a/chinadigitaltimes.net/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dFc0V1d0REQ4RkJ5d25uWFowVTNhWUE6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"328\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代 </a><br />\n